ianIsLost" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">filian | Vtuber in training</a> ／ <a href="https://twitch.tv/filian" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">filian</a> ／ <a href="https://www.mythictalent.com/creators/filian" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Filian</a></p> <cite>YouTube / Twitter / Twitch / Mythic Talent</cite> </blockquote><p></p><div class="rygqq64b5a16eb8093" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
